ore":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"一早都講左<br />\n但係佢地不斷拖<br />\n拖到時機過左就無人支持架啦<br />\n自己條命都咁兒戲，邊個救到佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"你唔知工會有幾多人做緊野就屌人慢..如果每個人都自己罷工使乜入工會<br />\n幾個月前已經win左啦 你坐係度做軍師請問有咩貢獻 <br />\n不指責只係口講? 睇唔睇到有po話跟本唔夠人手做野? 話即刻就即刻?"},{"pid":"d6d60944e802bb5348e79dcc4aefb0e9fa33ac77","tid":1846403,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102af60d5e842957fa4eaa7276fcd559cb3dcc91","tid":1846403,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:18.000Z","msg":"岩，要罷趁早，成功爭取封關之後減少好多工作壓力"},{"pid":"6b2dd11d1b31fe69ea581e36b3b57d2533539285","tid":1846403,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df1fd86b59b868a185aeb456c250b37231aaa942","tid":1846403,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:24:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c64b92ec1d17b3525c3f9546305266dc5de892a","tid":1846403,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46621b838fc704b3b8cf3141d566852c362bec0","tid":1846403,"uid":91603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:30:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c8f00b3fcd59abf55ea12911a5836072d3ebcfc","tid":1846403,"uid":120983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:30:59.000Z","msg":"Timing真係好重要<br />\n呢一刻藍屍歸哂我地邊係因為佢地未中招<br />\n而支那狗又來勢洶洶 港共就睇死你班愚民惡唔出樣<br />\n他日社區爆發班藍屍一定寧願同支那攬炒都一定抗議醫護罷工"},{"pid":"1b41fbf6c1f93bc862feb03d4d33cce44bad08a7","tid":1846403,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:32:41.000Z","msg":"我懇求大家無論用任何方法都要留返條命 港共想將香港人種族清洗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846903</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"63ee8ed8086013c5a2d87b961a2b49d77f25b4b5","tid":1846403,"uid":195827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"459282a11defeaf02dbfdd3a5165ab9f4631edb3","tid":1846403,"uid":195827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:34:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aba6bb73fad4ff7101f7059c44102c3e283faf6a","tid":1846403,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:37:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1838540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1838540</a><br />\n<br />\n三日前一早講左<br />\n班智障話工會程序神聖